    <div class="faq-a" id="does-google-penalize-ai-written-content"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google does not penalize AI content for being AI. Google's <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/blog/2023/02/google-search-and-ai-content">helpful content guidance</a> is explicit that AI use is permitted when the content is helpful, original, and authored with experience. Google does penalize unhelpful content, regardless of whether a human or AI wrote it. The dividing line is quality, not authorship.</p></div></div>
