    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="what-content-types-are-safe-for-ai"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Glossary entries, comparison pages, evergreen SEO guides, FAQ pages, product descriptions, social captions, metadata, alt text, and bulk content with high QC review are safe. The common pattern is low harm, low originality requirement, and clear factual scaffolding. These map to Tier 4 and Tier 5 in the risk pyramid.</p></div></div>
