      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="how-do-i-fact-check-ai-generated-content"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Run every stat, name, date, percentage, and citation against a primary source. Open a fresh browser tab for each claim. Discard any source the model invented. Replace fabricated stats with verified ones from named studies. The fact-check pass takes 10 to 20 minutes per 1,500-word post and is the single most important step in the editing workflow.</p></div></div>
